    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Oligopeptide-249 Oligopeptide-250 sh-Oligopeptide-2) is a single chain recombinant peptide produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the genes from Oligopeptide-249, Oligopeptide-250, and sh-Oligopeptide-2. The fusion peptide contains 107 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence from the 20 standard amino acids."
